	   <tr><td colspan=2> OK&nbsp;&nbsp; The idea of race specific items seems pretty cool , but there is a big problem with this item. 1) most melle that are capable of taking down inny, &quot;normally&quot; will have a haste item in the cloak spot in the first place i.e. cloak of flames / crystalline waters, seb cloak ect. not everyone, but alot of them. Secondly, as an iksar monk, this item really pisses me off being 1.0 weight, sure its not HEAVY, but they should have made this thing 0.1  or something close, i mean come on its off inny.  and 3rd and one of the biggest, this cloak isnt even iksar only anymore, which ALL of inny's drops are supposed to be. You see, when they added the the beastlord's with luclin alot of items got messed up. Basically what happend was this, if an item was usable by a race that BL's can be (for instance this cloak is supposed to be IKSAR ONLY), they messed up in the coding and instead of just adding BST to the usable class, they also added ALL the RACES that beastlords can be( all large races)  So to keep it simple this cloak should have been changed to:                Class : war,shd,mnk,shm,nec, BST<br>Race : Iksar <br><br>BUT, it wasnt, this is what it reads now<br><br>Class: war,shd,mnk,shm,nec,bst<br>Race: Bar,ogr,trl,iks,vah<br><br>now everytime this  Gdamn thing drops some iksar has to freaking roll against all the other races, while all the other items are fine adn some ogre war can actually wear this. how stupid, and i KNOW they are aware of this, but they are to busy being greedy with legends and other crap to fix it, bastuds. ok flame me if you want, that is the truth. if you dont belive me, look up some other IKSAR only items, they are all messed up, altho they have fixed some, but not others, helmet of rile from karnors was the same way till they fixed it. hope this info helps, and i hope someone sees this and gets the crap fixed.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
